[Twitter](https://twitter.com/HetorGG) | [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/hetorgg/)

A Mexican voice actor. He is known for being the Latin American Spanish voice of Kick Buttowski in *Kick Buttowski: Suburban Daredevil*, Richochet in *¡Mucha Lucha!* and Lex Luthor in the* DC Extended Universe*
He is the recurring dub voice of Zac Efron, T.J. Miller, Jesse Eisenberg, and Josh Gad.

He is married to [Karla Falcón](https://anilist.co/staff/181977/Karla-Falcn).
